I want my files to show up in

00:26:07.956 --> 00:26:11.616 A:middle
Recents and in Search.

00:26:12.456 --> 00:26:13.766 A:middle
Then you have a second tree,

00:26:14.166 --> 00:26:15.446 A:middle
which we call the physical tree,

00:26:16.046 --> 00:26:17.706 A:middle
which lets iOS know how the

00:26:17.706 --> 00:26:19.316 A:middle
files are represented on-disk.

00:26:20.216 --> 00:26:21.706 A:middle
And, here this is much simpler,

00:26:22.036 --> 00:26:23.556 A:middle
because you only have two

00:26:23.556 --> 00:26:23.926 A:middle
choices.

00:26:25.406 --> 00:26:27.556 A:middle
In most cases, you will be

00:26:27.556 --> 00:26:29.286 A:middle
