00:26:38.446 --> 00:26:40.446 A:middle
the file package, you're going

00:26:40.446 --> 00:26:42.006 A:middle
to use com.apple.package.

00:26:42.466 --> 00:26:43.536 A:middle
But, in most cases, you have a

00:26:43.536 --> 00:26:44.576 A:middle
single file disk, so it's

00:26:44.576 --> 00:26:45.926 A:middle
public.data.

00:26:47.656 --> 00:26:49.146 A:middle
This is because I am in with

